  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/34aa23463b8104adb7ab47982eedb80c.poster.avif?t=1673444229\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/34aa23463b8104adb7ab47982eedb80c.webm?t=1673444229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/34aa23463b8104adb7ab47982eedb80c.mp4?t=1673444229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>GLADIUM</strong> is an action game set in the Roman gladiatorial era. With a focus on brutal boss fights and a progression system based on blood and gold, you will have to embrace death to be victorious.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HEART POUNDING BOSS FIGHTS</h2>Challenge the unforgiving champions of the arena with their own unique mechanics and tactics!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACTION COMBAT</h2>Fast-paced action combat featuring dodging, parrying, special attacks and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GLADIATORS OF OLD</h2>Fight against enemy gladiators with appearance and behaviour based on the gladiator classes of ancient Rome, from the Murmillo to the Crupellarius!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PIT FIGHTING</h2>Get a random weapon and fight one versus one against another gladiator with his own random weapon!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS MODE</h2>Face never-ending waves of enemies and bosses with highscores. Display your blood-spilling ability with online leaderboards!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADES AND UNLOCKS</h2>Earn coins in the arena to purchase new weapons and shields - find your playstyle! <br>Unlock unique helmets offering diverse effects from completing various tasks!<br>Spend blood to unlock and customize the powers of your special attack!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/612495f642b79561408c146bdcc4840a.poster.avif?t=1673444229\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/612495f642b79561408c146bdcc4840a.webm?t=1673444229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/612495f642b79561408c146bdcc4840a.mp4?t=1673444229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
